CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 27, 1945, pg. 8, reads: "Deltas Confer - Delta Sigma Theta sorors gathered together last week to confer with Midwestern Regional Director Gwendolyn Higginbotham, who came on from Bluefield, W. Va. She was entertained at dinner at Loendi Club by members of Alpha Epsilon and Mu Chapters. Above she is shown, third from left, discussing sorority business with Soror Doris Handy, president of Mu Chapter; Soror Lillian Brown and Soror Helen Peeler, president of Alpha Epsilon Chapter. - Courier Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Delta Sigma Theta sorority members Doris Handy, Lillian Brown, Gwendolyn Higginbotham and Helen Peeler seated behind table in Loendi Club
